  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nTokio now has a stable version using stable futures and rust-libp2p has an open PR. The refactor of Lighthouse's networking code to use std futures and refactor'd for async/await will have drastic improvements for code readability. \r\n\r\nTransitioning to stable futures allows us to use async/await and take advantage of tokio's new features. ",
